fs = 256

# Create ECG widgets
segment_dropdown = widgets.Dropdown(
    options=events_df['name'].tolist(),
    value='baseline',
    description='Select Test Segment:',
    disabled=False,
)

process_method_dropdown = widgets.Dropdown(
    options=['neurokit', 'pantompkins1985', 'hamilton2002', 'elgendi2010', 'engzeemod2012'],
    value='neurokit',
    description="Select Cleaning Method:",
    disabled=False,
)

process_button = widgets.Button(
    description='Process ECG',
    disabled=False,
    button_style='',
    tooltip='Click to process the selected segment',
    icon='check'
)

output = widgets.Output()

def process_ecg():
    """Process ECG and store results in global variables"""
    global ecg_signals, ecg_info, analyzed_ecg_df
    
    selected_interval = events_df[events_df['name'] == segment_dropdown.value].iloc[0]
    start_time = selected_interval['start']
    end_time = selected_interval['end']
    
    start_idx = int((start_time - events_df['start'].min()).total_seconds() * fs)
    end_idx = int((end_time - events_df['start'].min()).total_seconds() * fs)
    
    ecg_segment = synched_df['ECG'][start_idx:end_idx]
    
    ecg_signals, ecg_info = nk.ecg_process(
        ecg_segment, 
        sampling_rate=fs, 
        method=process_method_dropdown.value
    )
    
    analyzed_ecg_df = nk.ecg_analyze(ecg_signals, sampling_rate=fs)
    
    with output:
        output.clear_output()
        display(analyzed_ecg_df)
        nk.ecg_plot(ecg_signals, ecg_info)

def on_ecg_button_click(b):
    process_ecg()

process_button.on_click(on_ecg_button_click)

display(segment_dropdown, process_method_dropdown, process_button, output)

def process_eda():
    """Process EDA and store results in global variables"""
    global eda_signals, eda_info, analyzed_eda_df
    
    selected_interval = events_df[events_df['name'] == eda_segment_dropdown.value].iloc[0]
    start_time = selected_interval['start']
    end_time = selected_interval['end']
    
    start_idx = int((start_time - events_df['start'].min()).total_seconds() * fs)
    end_idx = int((end_time - events_df['start'].min()).total_seconds() * fs)

Change Point Detection¶

In [28]:
import warnings
window_size = 60 * fs 

hrv_time_results = []
hrv_frequency_results = []
hrv_nonlinear_results = []
ptt_results = []


def process_hrv_ptt_eda(segment_name):
    """Process HRV, PTT, and EDA using a windowed approach and store results in global variables"""
    global hrv_time_results, hrv_frequency_results, ptt_results, eda_signals
    
    selected_interval = events_df[events_df['name'] == segment_name].iloc[0]
    start_time = selected_interval['start']
    end_time = selected_interval['end']
    
    start_idx = int((start_time - events_df['start'].min()).total_seconds() * fs)
    end_idx = int((end_time - events_df['start'].min()).total_seconds() * fs)
    
    ecg_segment = synched_df['ECG'][start_idx:end_idx]
    ppg_segment = synched_df['PPG'][start_idx:end_idx]
    eda_segment = synched_df['EDA'][start_idx:end_idx]
    
    # Process ECG, PPG, and EDA signals
    ecg_signals, ecg_info = nk.ecg_process(ecg_segment, sampling_rate=fs, method='neurokit')
    ppg_signals, ppg_info = nk.ppg_process(ppg_segment, sampling_rate=fs, method='elgendi')
    eda_signals, eda_info = nk.eda_process(eda_segment, sampling_rate=fs, method='neurokit')
    
    peaks_ecg = ecg_info['ECG_R_Peaks']
    peaks_ppg = ppg_info['PPG_Peaks']
    
    hrv_time_results = []
    hrv_frequency_results = []
    ptt_results = []
    ibi_results = []
    
    for start in range(0, len(ecg_segment), window_size):
        end = start + window_size
        if end > len(ecg_segment):
            break
        
        window_peaks_ecg = peaks_ecg[(peaks_ecg >= start) & (peaks_ecg < end)]
        window_peaks_ppg = peaks_ppg[(peaks_ppg >= start) & (peaks_ppg < end)]
        
        if len(window_peaks_ecg) > 1:
            hrv_time = nk.hrv_time(window_peaks_ecg, sampling_rate=fs)
            hrv_frequency = nk.hrv_frequency(window_peaks_ecg, sampling_rate=fs)
            
            hrv_time_results.append(hrv_time)
            hrv_frequency_results.append(hrv_frequency)
            
            ibis = np.diff(window_peaks_ecg) / fs
            ibi_results.append(pd.DataFrame(ibis, columns=['IBI']))
        
        for peak_ecg in window_peaks_ecg:
            subsequent_peaks_ppg = window_peaks_ppg[window_peaks_ppg > peak_ecg]
            if len(subsequent_peaks_ppg) > 0:
                peak_ppg = subsequent_peaks_ppg[0]
                ptt = (peak_ppg - peak_ecg) / fs
                ptt_results.append(ptt)
    
    hrv_time_results = pd.concat(hrv_time_results).reset_index(drop=True)
    hrv_frequency_results = pd.concat(hrv_frequency_results).reset_index(drop=True)
    ptt_results = pd.DataFrame(ptt_results, columns=['PTT'])
    ibi_results = pd.concat(ibi_results).reset_index(drop=True)
    
    prominent_features = {}
    if "HRV_LFHF" in hrv_frequency_results:
        prominent_features["ECG LF/HF"] = hrv_frequency_results["HRV_LFHF"]
    if not ibi_results.empty:
        prominent_features["ECG Inter Beat Intervals"] = ibi_results["IBI"]
    if "HRV_RMSSD" in hrv_time_results:
        prominent_features["ECG RMSSD"] = hrv_time_results["HRV_RMSSD"]
    if "HRV_MeanNN" in hrv_time_results:
        prominent_features["ECG Mean HR"] = hrv_time_results["HRV_MeanNN"]
    if "HRV_LFHF" in hrv_frequency_results:
        prominent_features["PPG LF/HF"] = hrv_frequency_results["HRV_LFHF"]
    prominent_features["PTT"] = ptt_results["PTT"]
    prominent_features["eda"] = eda_signals["EDA_Clean"]
    
    
    changepoints_results = {}
    for feature_name, feature_data in prominent_features.items():
        feature_data = feature_data.dropna()
        if not feature_data.empty and not feature_data.isnull().all():
            changepoints_results[feature_name] = nk.signal_changepoints(feature_data, change='meanvar', show=True)
            plt.title(feature_name)
    
    display(hrv_time_results)
    display(hrv_frequency_results)
    display(ptt_results)
    display(ibi_results)
    for feature_name, changepoints in changepoints_results.items():
        print(f"Changepoints in {feature_name}: {changepoints}")
    
    return prominent_features, changepoints_results

fig, axes = plt.subplots(len(prominent_features), 1, figsize=(10, 5 * len(prominent_features)))
if len(prominent_features) == 1:
    axes = [axes]

for ax, (feature_name, feature_data) in zip(axes, prominent_features.items()):
    ax.plot(feature_data)
    for cp in common_changepoints:
        ax.axvline(x=cp, color='r', linestyle='--')
    ax.set_title(feature_name)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
